info.title: Actions for &AKA; using &AWS; SDKs
info.titleabbrev: Actions

abstract.para: The following code examples show how to use &AKA; with &AWS; SDKs.

section.para: The following code examples demonstrate how to perform individual &AKA; actions with &AWS; SDKs. These excerpts call the &AKA; API and are not intended to be run in isolation. Each example includes a link to GitHub, where you can find instructions on how to set up and run the code in context.
The following examples include only the most commonly used actions. For a complete list, see the &AKA; API Reference.
